OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy and breezy for much of
OL,6,Fthe day with spells of rain at times,
OL,7,Fmostly affecting western hills with
OL,8,Fsomewhat drier conditions further
OL,9,Feast. Temperatures gradually
OL,10,Fincreasing and becoming warm.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FRemaining cloudy overnight
OL,13,Fwith low cloud as further patchy rain
OL,14,Fmoves eastwards, hill fog possible
OL,15,Fover western hills. Breezy winds
OL,16,Fcontinue.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
