OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FMonday, cloudy with patchy
OL,6,Frain mostly affecting western hills,
OL,7,Fwith drier conditions further east and
OL,8,Fsunny intervals along the coast.
OL,9,FTemperatures becoming warmer.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,12,FTuesday, cloudy to start with sunny
OL,13,Fintervals later. Wednesday and
OL,14,FThursday becoming sunnier and dry with
OL,15,Flight and variable winds. Temperatures
OL,16,Fvery warm.
